## Image Integration

### 1. Hero Image (Required)
**Use at the very top of the post:**
```html
<div class="not-prose mb-12">
  <div class="relative w-full h-[500px] md:h-[600px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-example?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop&q=80"
      alt="Detailed description of what the image shows"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="eager"
    />
  </div>
</div>
```

### 2. Full-Width Inline Image with Caption
**For major visual breaks and important illustrations:**
```html
<figure class="not-prose my-12">
  <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-example?w=1200&h=675&fit=crop&q=80"
      alt="Descriptive alt text"
      class="w-full h-auto"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
  <figcaption class="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-600 italic">
    Figure 1: Caption describing the image and providing context or data source
  </figcaption>
</figure>
```

### 3. Text-Wrapped Image (Inline)
**For smaller illustrations that complement paragraphs:**
```html
<div class="not-prose float-right ml-8 mb-6 w-full md:w-1/3">
  <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-example?w=500&h=375&fit=crop&q=80"
      alt="Descriptive alt text"
      class="w-full h-auto"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
  <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-600 italic text-center">Image caption</p>
</div>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
  Your paragraph text flows naturally around the image. This works well for product shots, diagrams, or supporting visuals that don't need full attention. The text wraps elegantly around the floating image on larger screens, while stacking on mobile for better readability.
</p>

<!-- Clear float after several paragraphs -->
<div class="clear-both"></div>
```

### 4. Side-by-Side Image Comparison
**Perfect for before/after, comparisons, or related concepts:**
```html
<div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-12">
  <figure>
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-example1?w=600&h=400&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="Before scenario"
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium text-center">
      Before: Description of initial state
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <figure>
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-example2?w=600&h=400&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="After scenario"
        class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <figcaption class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium text-center">
      After: Description of improved state
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
</div>
```

### 5. Image Gallery (3-4 images)
**For showcasing multiple related examples or perspectives:**
```html
<div class="not-prose my-12">
  <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-900">Gallery: Examples of [Topic]</h4>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1?w=400&h=300&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="Example 1"
        class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-2?w=400&h=300&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="Example 2"
        class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-3?w=400&h=300&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="Example 3"
        class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-4?w=400&h=300&fit=crop&q=80"
        alt="Example 4"
        class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 italic text-center">
    Collection caption explaining what these images demonstrate
  </p>
</div>
```

### 6. Image with Callout Box
**Combine visual and textual information:**
```html
<div class="not-prose my-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
  <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-example?w=700&h=500&fit=crop&q=80"
      alt="Key concept visualization"
      class="w-full h-auto"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-blue-500">
    <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-900">Key Insight</h4>
    <p class="text-lg text-blue-800 mb-4">
      Important takeaway or explanation that directly relates to the image shown. This combination helps reinforce the message through both visual and textual means.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-blue-800 space-y-2">
      <li>Supporting point 1</li>
      <li>Supporting point 2</li>
      <li>Supporting point 3</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
```

