## Deep Dive Components

### Research Citation Block
```html
<div class="not-prose my-8 bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-gray-400 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
  <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
    <span class="text-2xl">üìö</span>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Research Finding</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
        "Direct quote from research or study that supports your point and adds credibility to the deep dive content."
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
        ‚Äî Source Name, <em>Publication</em> (2024)
        <a href="https://source.com" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline ml-1">
          <sup>[1]</sup>
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Expert Quote/Pull Quote
```html
<blockquote class="not-prose my-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-transparent border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-8 rounded-r-xl">
  <p class="text-2xl font-serif italic text-gray-800 mb-4">
    "Compelling quote from an expert or authority that reinforces a key point in your deep dive. This should add weight and perspective to your analysis."
  </p>
  <footer class="flex items-center gap-4">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-expert?w=100&h=100&fit=crop&q=80"
      alt="Expert Name"
      class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div>
      <cite class="not-italic font-semibold text-gray-900">Expert Name</cite>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Title, Company/Institution</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</blockquote>
```

### Case Study Block
```html
<div class="not-prose my-12 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
  <div class="bg-green-500 px-8 py-4">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-3">
      <span>üìñ</span> Case Study: [Title]
    </h3>
  </div>

  <div class="p-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-700">85%</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Key Metric 1</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-700">$50K</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Key Metric 2</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-700">6 months</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Timeframe</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-green">
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>Background:</strong> Brief description of the situation or problem that was addressed.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>Approach:</strong> Explanation of the strategy or method used to tackle the challenge.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        <strong>Results:</strong> Specific outcomes and measurable impact of the solution.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Pro Tips Section
```html
<div class="not-prose my-12 bg-yellow-50 border-2 border-yellow-300 rounded-xl p-8">
  <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
    <span class="text-3xl">üí°</span> Pro Tips from the Experts
  </h4>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
      <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Tip #1: [Specific Tip]</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Detailed explanation of the tip and why it matters for readers implementing these strategies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-yellow-500">
      <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Tip #2: [Another Tip]</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">More actionable advice that adds practical value beyond the main content.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Timeline/Process Visualization
```html
<div class="not-prose my-12">
  <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8 text-gray-900 text-center">Step-by-Step Process</h4>

  <div class="relative">
    <!-- Vertical line -->
    <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-blue-200"></div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative flex items-start gap-6">
