## Navigation & Reading Experience

### Progress Indicator (Table of Contents)
```html
<div class="not-prose sticky top-4 mb-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-blue-100">
  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span>üìë</span> In This Deep Dive
  </h3>
  <nav class="space-y-2">
    <a href="#introduction" class="block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors">
      ‚Üí Introduction & Overview
    </a>
    <a href="#section-1" class="block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors">
      ‚Üí 1. [Section Title]
    </a>
    <a href="#section-2" class="block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors">
      ‚Üí 2. [Section Title]
    </a>
    <a href="#section-3" class="block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors">
      ‚Üí 3. [Section Title]
    </a>
    <a href="#conclusion" class="block text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors">
      ‚Üí Conclusion & Next Steps
    </a>
  </nav>
  <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 italic">Estimated reading time: 15 minutes</p>
</div>
```

### Section Navigation
```html
<section id="section-name" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-8">
  <div class="not-prose mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 border-b-4 border-blue-500 pb-4 inline-block">
      Section Title
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-4 italic">
      A brief overview of what this section covers and why it matters
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Section content with images and paragraphs -->
</section>
```

### Related Content Sidebar
```html
<div class="not-prose my-12 bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200">
